// PowerLaw(a) — Power Function distribution on [0, 1]
// Parameters: a > 0 (shape). Support: [0, 1].
// PDF: a·x^(a-1); CDF: x^a; Quantile: p^(1/a); Mean: a/(a+1)
// Variance: a/((a+1)²·(a+2)); Entropy: 1 - 1/a - ln(a)

